{
  "stem": "964.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I made some money over the week, so mother had money to buy bread.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then later on I-- when I was a, a-- older, I start to go in an apprenticeship to, to be a-- not a shoemaker.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "See, in Europe, they upper part from the-- from the shoes was one, one operation, and the lower part of the shoe, somebody else made it.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So this-- the lower part was a shoemaker.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The upper part was a [NON-ENGLISH], a upper part maker.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So I was working in the-- in that place learning the trade.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At work, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All this war, the cottage industry, everybody, you know, had one or two people working, all Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was all in Jewish hands.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, the Polish people-- this is from-- it's from generations back, they could smell a Jew.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They could smell a Jew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had this experience with them when, when the Germans invaded Poland.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "First of all, the name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then in the school, when, when, when they got up every day for the prayer, the Jews didn't get up.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I got beaten for why didn't I get up, help them with the prayer every day.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I got beaten for this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So this identify you, you already that you are Jewish.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Boy or girls, that doesn't matter.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We lived in a-- it was a three-story building.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So on the-- on the ground floor was a factory making-- what do you call it?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Bags.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Like you go to, to Publix, you have a shopping-- they put it in bags.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was a factory making bags.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "On the first-- On the second floor was the guy that I worked-- we used to work for him, Mr.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Kaufman.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And on the third floor already, people lived.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
